{{ 'what-inside.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="what-inside">
  <div class="what-inside__wrapper page-width section-top">
			
    <div class="what-inside__image">
      <img
        src="{{ 'bakuchiol-flower.png' | asset_url }}"
        width="640"
        height="640"
        alt="Bakuchiol flower, the plant-derived retinol alternative"
        loading="lazy"
      >
    </div>

    <div class="what-inside__content">
      <h2 class="what-inside__title section-title-bakuchiol">
        WHAT'S INSIDE?
      </h2>

      <ul class="what-inside__list">
        <li class="what-inside__item">
          <h3>BAKUCHIOL</h3>
          <p>
            PLANT-DERIVED RETINOL ALTERNATIVE THAT VISIBLY SOFTENS FINE LINES
            WITHOUT DRYNESS OR FLAKING
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="what-inside__item">
          <h3>PEPTIDE COMPLEX</h3>
          <p>
            TARGETED PEPTIDES THAT HELP SUPPORT FIRMNESS AND SMOOTH THE
            APPEARANCE OF WRINKLES OVER TIME
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="what-inside__item">
          <h3>HYDRATING LIPID BLEND</h3>
          <p>
            SKIN-MIMICKING OILS THAT REINFORCE THE MOISTURE BARRIER AND KEEP
            SKIN LOOKING PLUMP AND SUPPLE
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- SEO helper copy, visually hidden -->
  <div class="what-inside__sr-only">
    The Bakuchiol Age Delay Serum combines a gentle plant-derived retinol
    alternative with a peptide complex and hydrating lipids to soften fine
    lines, support firmness, and maintain a healthy moisture barrier for
    smoother, more radiant skin.
  </div>
</section>

